<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Events - Admin Maree</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bulma@1.0.4/css/bulma.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/adminstyle.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --event-cream: #f8f2ea;
            --event-sand: #e9dac7;
            --event-cocoa: #4a3426;
            --event-copy: #70584a;
            --event-accent: #c6674d;
            --event-accent-deep: #a64e39;
            --event-sage: #8aa57a;
            --event-sage-soft: #edf5e8;
            --event-line: #eadbca;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fffdfa 0%, #f7efe6 100%);
        }

        .events-shell {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-end;
            gap: 24px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
        }

        .events-kicker,
        .event-kicker {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 8px 14px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: rgba(198, 103, 77, 0.12);
            color: var(--event-accent-deep);
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 1.4px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .events-copy,
        .event-help-copy {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin-top: 14px;
            color: var(--event-copy);
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .events-toolbar {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .event-primary-button {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--event-accent) 0%, var(--event-accent-deep) 100%) !important;
            border: none !important;
            color: #fff !important;
            box-shadow: 0 18px 32px rgba(166, 78, 57, 0.2);
        }

        .event-primary-button:hover,
        .event-primary-button:focus {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #bc5c43 0%, #954430 100%) !important;
            color: #fff !important;
        }

        .button.event-ghost {
            border-color: var(--event-line);
            color: var(--event-copy);
            background: #fff;
        }

        .button.event-ghost:hover,
        .button.event-ghost:focus {
            border-color: var(--event-accent);
            color: var(--event-accent-deep);
            background: #fff7f3;
        }

        .button.event-danger {
            background: #b85f4c;
            border-color: #b85f4c;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .button.event-danger:hover,
        .button.event-danger:focus {
            background: #a15141;
            border-color: #a15141;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .event-card {
            border: 1px solid var(--event-line);
            border-radius: 24px;
            overflow: hidden;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #fff9f4 100%);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 38px rgba(88, 56, 36, 0.09);
            height: 100%;
        }

        .event-card.is-inactive {
            opacity: 0.85;
        }

        .event-card .card-content {
            padding: 28px;
        }

        .event-card .title {
            font-size: 32px !important;
            margin-bottom: 10px !important;
        }

        .event-card-head {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
        }

        .event-card-label {
            font-size: 11px;
            letter-spacing: 1.4px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #8d725d;
        }

        .event-status-pill {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            border-radius: 999px;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .event-status-pill.is-active {
            background: var(--event-sage-soft);
            color: #58704a;
        }

        .event-status-pill.is-inactive {
            background: #f8ebe5;
            color: #9b6256;
        }

        .event-description {
            min-height: 96px;
            color: var(--event-cocoa);
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .event-badges {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 18px;
        }

        .event-chip {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            border-radius: 999px;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            background: #f4e3d4;
            color: var(--event-accent-deep);
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .event-chip.secondary {
            background: #edf3e7;
            color: #59724c;
        }

        .event-date-tag {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 8px 14px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            border: 1px solid var(--event-line);
            background: #fff;
            color: var(--event-copy);
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .event-card-footer {
            border-top: 1px solid var(--event-line);
        }

        .event-footer-button {
            border: none;
            background: transparent;
            color: var(--event-accent-deep);
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
        }

        .event-footer-button:hover {
            background: #fff2ea;
        }

        .event-footer-button.is-danger-text {
            color: #b85f4c;
        }

        .event-footer-button.is-disabled,
        .event-footer-button:disabled {
            color: #bea08a;
            cursor: not-allowed;
            background: #faf3ed;
        }

        .event-help-box,
        .event-modal-box {
            border: 1px solid var(--event-line);
            border-radius: 26px !important;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fffdf9 0%, #f8efe4 100%);
            box-shadow: 0 24px 50px rgba(78, 54, 28, 0.08);
            color-scheme: light;
        }

        .event-help-title {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.8px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--event-accent-deep);
        }

        .event-modal-box .title {
            font-size: 38px !important;
        }

        .events-form-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 18px;
        }

        .events-form-grid .field.is-full {
            grid-column: 1 / -1;
        }

        .input,
        .textarea {
            border-color: var(--event-line);
            background-color: #fff8f2;
            color: var(--event-cocoa);
            box-shadow: none;
        }

        .input::placeholder,
        .textarea::placeholder {
            color: #9d7d65;
        }

        .input[type="date"] {
            color-scheme: light;
        }

        .input[type="date"]::-webkit-calendar-picker-indicator {
            opacity: 0.85;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .input:focus,
        .textarea:focus {
            border-color: var(--event-accent);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.125em rgba(198, 103, 77, 0.18);
        }

        .label,
        .event-checkbox {
            color: var(--event-cocoa);
        }

        .event-checkbox {
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .helper-note {
            color: #8a735e;
            font-size: 12px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-top: 6px;
        }

        .event-selection-box {
            min-height: 180px;
            max-height: 240px;
            overflow-y: auto;
            border: 1px dashed var(--event-line);
            border-radius: 18px;
            padding: 14px;
            background: #fffdfa;
        }

        .event-selection-box.event-box-error {
            border-color: #b85f4c;
            background: #fff5f1;
        }

        .event-option {
            display: block;
            padding: 8px 0;
            color: var(--event-copy);
        }

        .event-selected-summary {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 8px;
            min-height: 42px;
        }

        .modal-background {
            background: rgba(74, 52, 38, 0.5);
        }

        .is-centered-copy {
            margin-inline: auto;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .events-form-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .event-card .title,
            .event-modal-box .title {
                font-size: 30px !important;
            }

            .events-toolbar {
                width: 100%;
                justify-content: space-between;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="events-shell">
                <div>
                    <span class="events-kicker">Eventos, promociones y catalogo</span>
                    <h1 class="title">Catalogo de Eventos</h1>
                    <p class="events-copy">
                        Administra eventos vigentes, sus fechas, estado y los productos o promociones
                        que participan en cada experiencia de Maree.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="events-toolbar">
                    <a href="/admin" class="button event-ghost is-medium" type="button">
                        Volver al dashboard
                    </a>
                    <div id="loading-spinner" class="button is-loading is-ghost is-hidden"></div>
                    <button id="btn-nuevo-evento" class="button event-primary-button is-rounded is-medium" type="button">
                        Nuevo evento
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div id="contenedor-eventos" class="columns is-multiline"></div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section pt-0">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="box event-help-box">
                <p class="event-help-title">Gestion de Eventos</p>
                <p class="event-help-copy">
                    Las altas y modificaciones validan vigencia y al menos una relacion activa con promociones
                    o productos. Tambien puedes desactivar un evento sin perder su historial o eliminarlo
                    por completo cuando ya no sea necesario.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="modal" id="modal-evento">
        <div class="modal-background" data-close-modal="modal-evento"></div>
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="box event-modal-box">
                <form id="form-evento" novalidate>
                    <input type="hidden" id="id_evento">

                    <div class="events-form-grid">
                        <div class="field is-full">
                            <span class="event-kicker" id="kicker-modal-evento">Registro administrativo</span>
                            <h3 class="title is-4 mt-4" id="titulo-modal-evento">Registrar Nuevo Evento</h3>
                            <p class="helper-note" id="descripcion-modal-evento">
                                Captura el evento, define su vigencia y selecciona las promociones o productos vinculados.
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="field">
                            <label class="label" for="nombre">Nombre</label>
                            <div class="control">
                                <input id="nombre" class="input" type="text" maxlength="100" placeholder="Ej. Noche de Crepas">
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="field">
                            <label class="label">Estado</label>
                            <label class="checkbox event-checkbox">
                                <input type="checkbox" id="activo" checked>
                                Evento activo en catalogo
                            </label>
                        </div>

                        <div class="field is-full">
                            <label class="label" for="descripcion">Descripcion</label>
                            <div class="control">
                                <textarea id="descripcion" class="textarea" rows="3" placeholder="Describe el concepto del evento, sus reglas o el contexto general."></textarea>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="field">
                            <label class="label" for="fechaInicio">Fecha de Inicio</label>
                            <div class="control">
                                <input id="fechaInicio" class="input" type="date">
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="field">
                            <label class="label" for="fechaFin">Fecha de Fin</label>
                            <div class="control">
                                <input id="fechaFin" class="input" type="date">
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="field is-full">
                            <label class="label">Promociones vinculadas</label>
                            <div id="lista-promociones" class="event-selection-box">
                                <p class="has-text-grey">Cargando catalogo...</p>
                            </div>
                            <p class="helper-note">
                                Puedes ligar una o varias promociones activas o historicas al evento.
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="field is-full">
                            <label class="label">Resumen de promociones</label>
                            <div id="resumen-promociones" class="event-selected-summary">
                                <span class="event-chip">Sin promociones seleccionadas</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="field is-full">
                            <label class="label">Productos vinculados</label>
                            <div id="lista-productos" class="event-selection-box">
                                <p class="has-text-grey">Cargando catalogo...</p>
                            </div>
                            <p class="helper-note">
                                Agrega los productos especiales o afectados por el evento.
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="field is-full">
                            <label class="label">Resumen de productos</label>
                            <div id="resumen-productos" class="event-selected-summary">
                                <span class="event-chip secondary">Sin productos seleccionados</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="buttons is-right mt-5">
                        <button type="button" class="button event-ghost" data-close-modal="modal-evento">Cancelar</button>
                        <button type="submit" class="button event-primary-button" id="boton-guardar-evento">Guardar evento</button>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="modal-resultado" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-background" data-close-modal="modal-resultado"></div>
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="box event-modal-box has-text-centered">
                <span class="event-kicker" id="kicker-modal-resultado">Actualizacion de eventos</span>
                <h3 class="title is-4 mt-4" id="titulo-modal-resultado">Operacion completada</h3>
                <p id="mensaje-modal-resultado" class="events-copy is-centered-copy">
                    El evento se proceso correctamente.
                </p>
                <button class="button event-primary-button mt-5" type="button" id="boton-modal-resultado">Continuar</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="modal-confirmar-desactivacion" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-background" data-close-modal="modal-confirmar-desactivacion"></div>
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="box event-modal-box">
                <span class="event-kicker">Estado de eventos</span>
                <h3 class="title is-4 mt-4" id="titulo-confirmar-estado-evento">Cambiar estado de evento</h3>
                <p id="mensaje-confirmar-desactivar" class="events-copy">
                    Deseas desactivar este evento? Permanecera registrado, pero dejara de mostrarse como activo.
                </p>
                <div class="buttons is-right mt-5">
                    <button type="button" class="button event-ghost" data-close-modal="modal-confirmar-desactivacion">Cancelar</button>
                    <button type="button" class="button event-primary-button" id="boton-confirmar-desactivar">Confirmar cambio</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="modal-confirmar-eliminacion" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-background" data-close-modal="modal-confirmar-eliminacion"></div>
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="box event-modal-box">
                <span class="event-kicker">Eliminacion de eventos</span>
                <h3 class="title is-4 mt-4">Eliminar evento</h3>
                <p id="mensaje-confirmar-eliminar" class="events-copy">
                    Deseas eliminar este evento? Esta accion no se puede deshacer.
                </p>
                <div class="buttons is-right mt-5">
                    <button type="button" class="button event-ghost" data-close-modal="modal-confirmar-eliminacion">Cancelar</button>
                    <button type="button" class="button event-danger" id="boton-confirmar-eliminar">Eliminar evento</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="/js/promos_eventos/eventos.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
